snippet.title: [PSX] Fighting Force 2 - Full Game Walkthrough / Longplay - Original Hardware
snippet.description:
(NOT Emulator) running through Open Source Scan Converter (OSSC) and Elgato HD60 S+

Fighting Force 2: Full Game: Longplay

All levels and bosses

So in this longplay I beat Fighting Force 2 on PS1, this was one of the first games I played in my entire life, so it wasn't such a difficult task, this longplay marks the beginning of many games to come!

If you liked this longplay, leave your like and subscribe (leave in the comments the games you want to see here on the channel)

00:00:00  Intro
00:02:49  Steel Mill
00:40:58  Research Lab 
01:01:15  Tank Factory
01:46:53  Polar Base
02:07:46  Jungle Temple 
02:23:49  Prison Island
03:01:07  Undersea Base
03:19:50  Skyscraper
03:49:50  Credits/Ending 

Thank you for watching!

By: PSX CODEX
